import './Blast.css' import axios from 'axios' import { useForm } from 'react-hook-form' import {useEffect, useState} from 'react' const Blast = () => { const {register, handleSubmit} = useForm() const [databases, getDatabases] = useState() const getBlastDb = () => { axios.get(`http://192.168.1.37:8080/db/blast-db`).then(res => { getDatabases(res.data.map(entry => { return })) }) } useEffect(getBlastDb, []) const sendRequest = (data, service) => { let form = new FormData() Object.keys(data.files).map(file => form.append("file", data.files[file])) form.append("data", { data }) axios.post(`http://192.168.1.37:8080/services/${service}`, {data}, { headers: { "Content-type":"multipart/form-data" } }) .then() .catch() } return (
sendRequest(data,'blast')) }>
) } export default Blast
